gpio: mpc8xxx: Convert mpc8xxx_gpio_chip.lock to raw_spinlock

mpc8xxx_gpio_chip.lock needs to be a real spinlock in preempt-rt.
Especially the interrupt related functions can not be converted to a
sleeping lock.

